        <h2>About This Application</h2>
        <p>This project was created for the Dynamic Web Apps module at Goldsmiths, University of London. The aim is to consolidate learnings from the labs into a single, functional web application centered around the theme of health and fitness.</p>
        
        <h3>Technology Stack Used:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>**Backend:** Node.js and Express</li>
            <li>**Templating:** EJS</li>
            <li>**Database:** MySQL</li>
            <li>**Security:** `bcrypt` for password hashing (Additional Technique)</li>
            <li>**Validation:** `express-validator` and `express-sanitizer` (Additional Technique)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>The application is deployed to the Goldsmiths virtual server environment and all code is shared via GitHub.</p>
